 Amanda dates and intends to marry, and he’s willing to go to extraordinary lengths to get it when it comes to bad behavior.  Will Walter’s antics prevent Amanda from finding true love? Can she control the monstrous mastiff’s outrageous conduct and get him to accept the man she loves?  The answers will surprise you, as they prove once again that love sometimes comes to us from the most unlikely directions, and quite often when we least expect it.  Bob McCullough is a #1 Amazon Bestselling author who has written bestsellers in several different genres, with romance among the most prominent.  In “The Wedding Dog,” his fifth dog-based romance, he’s created a charming canine narrator, and a winning protagonist in Amanda Peters. The result is a satisfying trip to romantic heaven for hardcore romantics, so download this book NOW and let the romantic fun begin!<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"16598498953651672311\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'25_book_51710686\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"MGPh++J+Zycgb7HGiWYh6khA/LUajoO6liSc7+SO5yipxDZ63587QDwrAFKEx5LiCvCDYNJEgdhkhK4j7Mzc/g==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"51710686\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"25_book_51710686\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"h